tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE solar_panel_efficiency_ratings (
    panel_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    efficiency_rating FLOAT NOT NULL,
    manufacturer TEXT NOT NULL,
    installation_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE panel_installations (
	installation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	panel_id INT,
	installation_date DATE,
	location VARCHAR(100),
	FOREIGN KEY (panel_id) REFERENCES solar_panels(panel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE panel_maintenance (
	maintenance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	installation_id INT,
	maintenance_date DATE,
	maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
	FOREIGN KEY (installation_id) REFERENCES panel_installations(installation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE PanelInstallations (
    installation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_id INT,
    installation_date DATE,
    location VARCHAR(100),
    FOREIGN KEY(panel_id) REFERENCES SolarPanels(panel_id)
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    installation_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    description TEXT,
    FOREIGN KEY(installation_id) REFERENCES PanelInstallations(installation_id)
);

CREATE TABLE WarrantyDetails (
    warranty_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    panel_id INT,
    warranty_start DATE,
    warranty_end DATE,
    warranty_provider VARCHAR(100),
    FOREIGN KEY(panel_id) REFERENCES SolarPanels(panel_id)
);
